    <h2>Upload images, audio and video</h2>
    
    <p>Upload new images, audio or video into the library. To upload new media content, create an event with title and description and upload your files.</p>

    <form action="@@image-library-upload" method="post">
        <div class="field"><label>Title</label><br/> 
            <input type="text" name="title"> 
        </div>
        <div class="field"><label>Description</label>
            <textarea name="description"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-controls">
            <input type="submit" name="form.button.add_image_folder" value="Add Image Folder">
            <input type="submit" name="form.button.add_audio_folder" value="Add Audio Folder">
            <input type="submit" name="form.button.add_video_folder" value="Add Video Folder">
        </div>
    </form>
    
    <h2>Tag existing media</h2>

    <p>You can tag media by using the bulk tagger, where you can quickly tag multiple objects without reloading the page. 
        Select an event you want to tag:</p>
        
    <form action="image-library-tag-event" method="post">
        <select name="event" onchange="window.location=this.options[this.selectedIndex].getAttributeNode('value').value+'/@@bulk_tagger'">
            <option tal:repeat="te view/taggable_events" tal:attributes="value te/value" tal:content="te/content"></option>
        </select>
    </form>
    
